reviews.text: Shopping mall and very yummy food as well
The shopping mall has Small and Medium business asking from pharmacy items to hardware items. Not very crowded but everything one would need it there, there is a Kai Bo super market on ground floor.
This is a wonderful program, because it brought many experienced people from diverse background, from CEOs to partners of Big 4 to CFOs to entrepreneurs.”

Mall has hourly parking. Good for simple dinning at affordable price, quite a few choices there. Plenty of banks and ATM machines in the mall. Close to Wetland Park. The closest light rail station is Tin Sau Station.
